## Technical Details

### Robot Model вҖ” ABB IRB120

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| DOF | 6 revolute joints |
| Payload | 3 kg |
| Reach | 580 mm |
| J1 range | Вұ165В° |
| J2 range | Вұ110В° |
| J3 range | Вұ70В° |
| J4 range | Вұ160В° |
| J5 range | Вұ120В° |
| J6 range | Вұ400В° |
| Force/torque sensor offset | 82.25 mm from flange |
| Pusher finger length | 110 mm |

Control gains: kp = 200 / kv = 100 (joints 1вҖ“3); kp = 100 / kv = 50 (joints 4вҖ“6)

### Inverse Kinematics

Three solvers are implemented in `robot_controller.py`:

| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| Newton-Raphson | Standard Jacobian-based iteration |
| **Damped Least Squares** (default) | J^T (JJ^T + О»ВІI)^{-1} вҖ” robust near singularities |
| Gradient Descent | Step-based minimization of pose error |

The damping coefficient О» is adjusted dynamically based on the convergence rate to balance accuracy and singularity avoidance.

### CoM Estimation вҖ” Physics Model

The tipping maneuver produces a time series of contact force **F**(t) and object rotation angle Оё(t). The model parameters m (mass) and z_c (CoM height) are recovered by minimizing:

```
min_{m, z_c}  ||П„_app(t) вҲ’ П„_grav(Оё(t), m, z_c)||ВІ
```

where:
- **П„_app** = r_f Г— F вҖ” applied torque from finger contact
- **П„_grav** = вҲ’r_c Г— R(вҲ’Оё) В· W вҖ” gravity torque about the tipping edge
- **r_c** = [d_x, d_y, z_c]бөҖ вҖ” CoM position vector from pivot
- **R(вҲ’Оё)** вҖ” rotation matrix for object angle about the tipping axis

Fitting is performed with `scipy.optimize.curve_fit` (Levenberg-Marquardt).

### Signal Processing

Raw force signals are passed through a three-stage filter cascade:

1. **Butterworth low-pass** вҖ” 4th order, 5 Hz cutoff (removes high-frequency vibration)
2. **Median filter** вҖ” kernel size 5 (removes impulse artifacts)
3. **Savitzky-Golay** вҖ” 3rd order polynomial, kernel size 89 (smooths while preserving tipping transient shape)

### Test Objects

| Object | Ground Truth Mass | Ground Truth z_c | Notes |
|--------|:-----------------:|:----------------:|-------|
| Box | 664 g | 146 mm | Uniform rectangular prism |
| Heart | 236 g | 98 mm | Irregular geometry |
| Flashlight | 387 g | 97 mm | Cylindrical, off-axis mass |
| L-shape | 106 g | 58 mm | Asymmetric cross-section |
| Monitor | 5008 g | 252 mm | Large, heavy object |
| Soda can | 2071 g | 115 mm | Cylindrical, near-uniform |

### Simulation Parameters

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| Timestep | 1 ms (1 kHz) |
| Integrator | Implicit-fast |
| Gravity | 9.81 m/sВІ |
| Table friction | Ој = 1.0 |
| Experiment sample rate | 500 Hz |

